Mail XForms Engine
------------------

This add-on for Mozilla Thunderbird 3 permits to use XForms-based forms
in compose window and read panels in order to send information through email headers.

Forms are written with the XForms XML language embedded into XHTML or XUL files and
are provided by one or several customized "Mail XForms Data" add-ons.


Mozilla XForms add-on is required.


This add-on is written in XUL and Javascript.

Trustedbird/Milimail project
